== 交通 ==
身為[[剛果河|剛果河]]沿岸最重要的河港，水路運輸對於金夏沙有舉足輕重的地位，在剛果河岸的[[恩戈比拉河灘|恩戈比拉河灘]]（Beach Ngobila），每日都有[[渡輪|渡船]]前往布拉柴維爾或[[班基|班基]]（[[中非共和國|中非共和國]]首都）等同樣都位於剛果河岸的大城市。

陸運方面，為了便利利文斯通瀑布上下游的貨物運輸，在19世紀末就修築了[[馬塔迪-金沙薩鐵路|馬塔迪-金沙薩鐵路]]連結金夏沙與馬塔迪。金夏沙的[[機場|主機場]]為[[恩吉利國際機場|恩吉利國際機場]]，是該國境內四座[[國際機場|國際機場]]中規模最大者。

==文化==
金沙萨以[[法语|法语]]作為[[官方语言|官方语言]]，[[林加拉语|林加拉语]]則是日常[[通用语|通用语]]，在全球[[法语圈|法语圈]]中該城是僅次於[[巴黎|巴黎]]的第二大城市<ref>{{cite book |url=http://books.google.fr/books?id=Le_8WMk1Pr4C&lpg=PA111&dq=french%20lingala%20kinshasa&pg=PA103#v=onepage&q&f=false |title=Globalization and Language Vitality: Perspectives from Africa, pp. 103 & 109 |author=Cécile B. Vigouroux & Salikoko S. Mufwene |accessdate=2012-06-25}}</ref>。如果按照目前的人口趋势，到2020年，金沙萨的人口将超过巴黎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://esa.un.org/unpd/wup/CD-ROM/WUP2011-F11a-30_Largest_Cities.xls |title=Time series of the population of the 30 largest urban agglomerations in 2011 ranked by population size, 1950-2025 |publisher=United Nations, Population Division |format=XLS |accessdate=2012-06-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120704051126/http://esa.un.org/unpd/wup/CD-ROM/WUP2011-F11a-30_Largest_Cities.xls |archivedate=2012-07-04 }}</ref>。2012年10月，第14届[[法語圈國際組織|法語圈國際組織]]峰会在金沙萨召开<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.francophonie.org/XIVe-Sommet-de-la-Francophonie,36849.html |title=XIVe Sommet de la Francophonie |publisher=[[Organisation_internationale_de_la_Francophonie|OIF]] |accessdate=2012-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120619065536/http://www.francophonie.org/XIVe-Sommet-de-la-Francophonie,36849.html |archive-date=2012-06-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

==社會問題==
===犯罪===
自[[第二次剛果戰爭|第二次剛果戰爭]]，金沙薩一直都沒能從戰亂中恢復，也因此一直是非洲最不安全的城市之一。其[[貧民窟|貧民窟]]中有大量[[黑幫|黑幫]]。[[走私|走私]]、[[搶劫|搶劫]]、[[強姦|強姦]]、[[綁架|綁架]]和幫派[[暴力|暴力]]屢見不鮮<ref name="安全"/>。金沙薩的自殺率也極高，每十萬人中就有112人自殺<ref>[http://africacenter.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/AfricaBrief-7.pdf 1 Nonstate Policing: Expanding the Scope for Tackling Africa’s Urban Violence] {{Wayback|url=http://africacenter.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/AfricaBrief-7.pdf |date=20111005100432 }} AFRICA SECURITY BRIEF</ref>。

===流浪兒===
金沙薩有許多孤兒流浪街頭<ref>[http://streetkidnews.blogsome.com/category/1/africa/congo-dr/ World Street Children News :: Congo (DR) Streetkid News] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100903033957/http://streetkidnews.blogsome.com/category/1/africa/congo-dr/ |date=2010-09-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Manson|first=Katrina|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE66L2TB20100722?sp=true|title=Congo's children battle witchcraft accusations|agency=Reuters|date=22 July 2010|accessdate=14 March 2011|archive-date=2019-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701030844/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-congo-democratic-witches/congos-children-battle-witchcraft-accusations-idUSTRE66L2TB20100722?sp=true|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並被警察、軍隊虐待。金沙薩街頭18歲以下的流浪兒約有兩萬，其中一半成了乞丐，四分之一做地攤生意還有三分之一在某種程度上接受僱傭<ref>{{cite web|url=http://africaaction.typepad.com/justafrica/2009/07/african-street-children-kinshasa-drc.html|title=Street Children in Kinshasa|publisher=Africa Action|date=8 July 2009|accessdate=14 March 2011|archive-date=2011-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811051604/http://africaaction.typepad.com/justafrica/2009/07/african-street-children-kinshasa-drc.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一些是因為戰爭緣故家庭破碎，還有些是因為被指控使用巫術而被驅逐<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.warchild.org.uk/our_projects/democratic_republic_of_congo/blog/child-witches-in-kinshasa|title=A night on the streets with Kinshasa's 'child witches'|publisher=War Child UK – Warchild.org.uk|accessdate=14 March 2011|archive-date=2011-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110212202739/http://www.warchild.org.uk/our_projects/democratic_republic_of_congo/blog/child-witches-in-kinshasa|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gvnet.com/streetchildren/Congo.htm|title=Danballuff – Children of Congo: From War to Witches(video)|publisher=Gvnet.com|accessdate=14 March 2011|archive-date=2011-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724075658/http://www.gvnet.com/streetchildren/Congo.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://english.people.com.cn/200706/01/eng20070601_379840.html |title=Africa Feature: Around 20,000 street children wander in Kinshasa |publisher=English.people.com.cn |date=1 June 2007 |accessdate=14 March 2011 |archive-date=2012-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017203028/http://english.people.com.cn/200706/01/eng20070601_379840.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gvnet.com/streetchildren/Congo.htm |title=Prevalence, Abuse & Exploitation of Street Children |publisher=Gvnet.com |accessdate=14 March 2011 |archive-date=2011-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724075658/http://www.gvnet.com/streetchildren/Congo.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

金沙薩的警察經常拘捕流浪兒，有時候這些流浪兒即使只犯了輕微的罪行，也會被警察射殺<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/1494555.stm |title=Police shoot dead street child in Kinshasa|publisher=BBC News|date=16 August 2001|accessdate=14 March 2011}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thenewslens.com/article/4603|title=或許不該被生下來：被內戰、愛滋、巫術迷信囚禁在街頭的金夏沙孩子|author=|last=Chi|first=Zou|date=2014-06-11|work=|newspaper=The News Lens 關鍵評論網|accessdate=2017-10-15|language=zh-TW}}</ref>。

